compressFolder

protected java.io.File compressFolder(java.io.File folder,
                                      java.io.File zipfile)
Compress a folder (recursively) to a given file. Empty folders are included. Known limitation : Non-ASCII characters such as ... are ZIP tools dependant. See : http://bugs.sun.com/bugdatabase/view_bug.do?bug_id=4244499 SUN ZIP implementation stores non-ASCII characters as UTF-8. JAVA_HOME/bin/jar.exe tool is able to unzip them. WinZip can't.

Parameters:
folder - File
zipfile - File
Returns:
File
